<h1>Growth</h1>

<p><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/History_of_Wikipedia"><img src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/33/Seigenthaler_effect.JPG" /></a></p>

<!--http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/b/b7/Seigenthaler_effect.gif-->


<p><i>You should follow me on twitter <a href="http://twitter.com/aaronsw">here</a>.</i></p>
<p class="posted">August 11, 2006</p>

